Forts.: 29 <Jan 71>*
The night as usual till two or three heat afterward some sleep in weting 5
shirts, the greatest troubel is now, when one siringe the woond, by the
great exertion to drow out the matters from the through he gets much head-
ach, after you had left on friday he wept saying I feel so elend, afterward
he said what would I do if you were not here, he is rather dijected, to day
29 specially. Emilia Gundert has sent him a basket of flowes with beautiful
italian grapes and a buquet with des violettes feichen which smell very
good. Dr Sick has not come since thursday, he is expected tomorrow.
